data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to live in Creekside Ridge. Spacious open floor plan with high ceilings, granite countertops, 42" cabinets, herringbone subway backsplash and island.  Ceramic tile floors, at entry, formal dining, breakfast, kitchen, utility room, 1/2bath & family room.  Grand entry with built in art niche, built in bookshelves & more, lots of natural lighting. Home has lots of space upstairs, game room and spacious bedrooms with walk in-closets. Nice covered patio, a must see to appreciate. Close to major highway and military base.
